{"componentChunkName":"component---src-page-post-tsx","path":"/turn-your-ship-around","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Markus Tacker","tagLine":"Software Crafter","description":"Software Crafter building üå©Ô∏è cloud-based cellular IoT solutions at Nordic Semiconductor.‚Äã\n\t\tMentor. Speaker. ‚ÄãConference & Community builder. Camper. üèïÔ∏è üöê","gitHubUrl":"https://github.com/coderbyheart/coderbyheart.com.git","siteUrl":"https://coderbyheart.com","twitter":"@coderbyheart","defaultCard":"https://images.ctfassets.net/bncv3c2gt878/3Jk4P6nFPNzaz1gsguktk8/350b7e4ddb2c7d86416243d9902920e2/social-card-default-2020.png"}}},"pageContext":{"page":{"id":"19dd8f11-0196-504b-8244-2390292bfc67","name":"turn-your-ship-around","relativeDirectory":"post","relativePath":"post/turn-your-ship-around.md","remark":{"htmlAst":{"children":[{"children":[{"properties":{"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/bncv3c2gt878/50mTdxTZqYwC3z2YYR8vyg/8ed8dae1fabe366ac4e695f125af6ab1/turn-your-ship-around.jpg?w=640&h=426","alt":"Turn Your Ship Around! by L. David Marquet"},"children":[],"tagName":"img","type":"element"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Turn Your Ship Around!"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://amzn.to/2hjslhx","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" by "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"L. David Marquet"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://www.davidmarquet.com/?utm_source=coderbyheart&utm_medium=blogpost&utm_campaign=turn-your-ship-around","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" is\nas concrete as it gets for books that promise changing your organization for the\nbetter."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Based on the famous book about his tour on the nuclear submarine USS Santa Fee,\nwhere Marquet faced the challenge of his career of becoming the commanding\nofficer on the worst performing ship in the entire US Navy but managed to turn\nit into the best performing within two years, the workbook lays out concrete\nexercises to implement what Marquet developed: intent-based leadership."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#intent-based-leadership","ariaLabel":"intent based leadership permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Intent-based leadership"}],"tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"intent-based-leadership","style":"position:relative;"},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"The method is essentially a helper to codify behavioral change throughout an\nentire organization. By making decisions observable by others it enables the\ntransfer of decision making power to \"lower\" levels; which is what you\nwant in any complex and complicated environment today. By "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"pushing authority to\ninformation"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":", as Marquet calls it, decisions are made where they need to be\nmade: where and when the action happens, and not many layers distant from it."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"The idea is simple: to have "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"leaders on every level"}],"tagName":"strong","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":", even at levels where\nindividuals are not used to lead. Obviously this skill is not inherently\nexistent everywhere in the organization so Marquet lays out the ideas and\nconcepts to equip them with mechanisms of "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Control"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" (put them in control of\ntheir actions and results), "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Competence"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" (give the the technical knowledge to\nmake the right decisions), and "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Clarity"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" (give the the understanding of the\norganization's purpose)."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"You will get more than two dozen exercises that can be executed in a few minutes\nand yield material for your team right away. The book is so applicable, that no\ntrainer is need, and there are companies that just by following the book, have\nsaved hundreds of million $."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"It not only tackles the common decision fatigue in organizations where it's more\nimportant to not make an error then to make a bold move but makes you discover\ninvisible red-tape, which alone are potentially limiting your ability to\ninnovate and create compelling products."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"The most important aspect of intent-based leadership in my opinion is that it\nestablishes deliberate learning towards a common goal which enables\norganizations to grow and become truly agile."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"}],"type":"root","data":{"quirksMode":false}},"frontmatter":{"title":"Turn Your Ship Around!","subtitle":"Book review","noheadline":null,"date":"2016-12-27T10:00+02:00","abstract":"The workbook to implement intent-based leadership in your organization\nis as concrete as it gets for books that promise changing your organization\nfor the better.\n","lang":null},"headings":[{"id":"intent-based-leadership","depth":2,"value":"Intent-based leadership"}]}},"Footer":{"id":"cfe5b9e2-511c-5615-992a-dab82e1f8ed7","name":"Footer","relativeDirectory":"","relativePath":"Footer.md","remark":{"htmlAst":{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Software Crafter building üå©Ô∏è cloud-based cellular IoT solutions at\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Nordic Semiconductor"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://nordicsemi.com/","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"."},{"children":[],"tagName":"br","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\nMentor. Speaker. Conference & Community builder. Camper. üèïÔ∏è üöê"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properti